<div class="story">  <p>The Gables is a condominium community of  ground level buildings that looking more like town houses situated on the west side of Rte 158 in Kitty Hawk. The Gables offer ground level living with room for visitors upstairs and a central location close to shopping and dining. The community consists of 13 duplex units and 26 property owners in the home owners association. The HOA takes care of the community pool. You will find The Gables nestled between the community of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/sandpiper-cay.asp" title="Sandpiper Cay">Sandpiper Cay</a> condos to the north and the subdivision of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/ted-wood-kitty-hawk-terrace.asp" title="Ted Wood Kitty Hawk Terrace">Ted Wood Kitty Hawk Terrace</a> to the south. </p> 
